OL,3,C'Cheeky' 4-year-old with half a heart
OL,4,Cswitches on his town's Christmas lights
OL,6,FA four-year-old boy from Cornwall, who
OL,7,Fwas born with half a heart, has
OL,8,Fswitched on the Christmas lights in
OL,9,FCamborne.
OL,11,FLouis Hood has a life-limiting
OL,12,Fcondition and has undergone three open
OL,13,Fheart surgeries in his short life.
OL,15,FAs a local hero, hundreds gathered to
OL,16,Fwatch him play his role in lighting up
OL,17,Fthe town's streets on Friday 29
OL,18,FNovember.
