OL,3,C'Cheeky' 4-year-old with half a heart
OL,4,Cswitches on his town's Christmas lights
OL,6,FHe enjoyed every moment in the
OL,7,Fspotlight, waving to the crowd and
OL,8,Fwishing them all a Happy Christmas.
OL,10,FJodie Hood, Louis' mother, said: "With
OL,11,FLouis and his special heart, hopefully
OL,12,Fhe is here forever, but every moment
OL,13,Fcounts.
OL,15,F"It's about making special memories
OL,16,Fwith him and this is one of those
OL,17,Fmoments we can really treasure.
