OL,3,C'Cheeky' 4-year-old with half a heart
OL,4,Cswitches on his town's Christmas lights
OL,6,F"Louis is a real cheeky chap, he loves
OL,7,Fto act out scenes from his favourite
OL,8,Fmovies. He's just such a character,
OL,9,Feveryone who meets him loves him.
OL,11,F"He really just lights up every room
OL,12,Fhe goes in."
OL,14,FOne of Louis' dreams is to go to
OL,15,FDisneyland and thanks to the local
OL,16,Fcommunity donating to Jodie's
OL,17,Ffundraiser, this dream will become a
OL,18,Freality before Christmas.
