OL,3,C'Cheeky' 4-year-old with half a heart
OL,4,Cswitches on his town's Christmas lights
OL,6,FJodie said she is so grateful to the
OL,7,Fpeople of Camborne and Redruth for
OL,8,Fsupporting her little boy.
OL,10,FCommenting on the festive evening,
OL,11,FAnna Pascoe, the manager of BID
OL,12,FCamborne, said: "This is all about the
OL,13,Fspirit of Christmas. It was so
OL,14,Fheartwarming to hear little Louis'
OL,15,Fstory.
OL,17,F"He is such a little showman and he
OL,18,Freally just wanted to make memories
OL,19,Fwith his family - and this has been
OL,20,Fpart of making his dream come true."
